Class ComplexNum

  • java.lang.Object
    • csci2540Assignment2.ComplexNum

  • public class ComplexNum
extends java.lang.Object
    ComplexNum is an object to represent a Complex number in form a + bi where the a and b are stored as doubled. In this case a is called the real number and b is called the imaginary number.
